{"tid":2049515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《5月35日》(庚子版) 粵語演出 今晚9：30","createTime":"2020-06-03T13:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T15:10:13.000Z","uid":29781,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"721e7537b8f3346d5c7ff9a22951a1d48ecaff69","tid":2049515,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p640x640/101506634_2585583141657768_5195794084555390976_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQl-QD4AFcpUZFcDnC-d0tt0rDwJ3x8V2uuYDyOkyWTvH69hJHdlp8bBt9C3TqL3MwA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=d8597f51df9696bd86b7b2842191b551&amp;oe=5EFD669C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp640x640%2F101506634_2585583141657768_5195794084555390976_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQl-QD4AFcpUZFcDnC-d0tt0rDwJ3x8V2uuYDyOkyWTvH69hJHdlp8bBt9C3TqL3MwA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3Dd8597f51df9696bd86b7b2842191b551%26oe%3D5EFD669C&h=42eedbd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一年伊始，雙雙步入八十歲的小林和阿大就迎來滿身病痛。兩個老人等待死亡，是再自然不過的事。<br />\n<br />\n只是，兩夫婦唯一的兒子哲哲三十年前死於不自然，許多事情到今日還沒有問出個明白來。<br />\n<br />\n小林期待從苦苦問責的歲月中解脫，相反一直膽小的阿大越想越不忿，以前顧著二人的晚年才不去抗爭，現在連老伴也快將離去，他還有什麼要害怕的？<br />\n<br />\n如是，他倆定下偉大的目標：在5月35日當天，要堂堂正正去拜祭兒子。<br />\n<br />\n在不正常國家的陽光底下做正常的事也是不合法的。<br />\n<br />\n「我們就去衝擊，這條不正常的底線。」阿大說。<br />\n<br />\n「老伴，我終於覺得你愛我了。」小林說。<br />\n<br />\n相約在5月35日，來個光明正大的紀念。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年6月3日<br />\n<br />\n時間：21:30-23:45 （香港時間）<br />\n<br />\n(演出約1小時50分鐘，演後設有座談會直播）<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stage64/live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstage64%2Flive%2F&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BDpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=d213e074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stage64/live/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CXRVMTjSGJ0&amp;feature=emb_err_woyt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCXRVMTjSGJ0%26feature%3Demb_err_woyt&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BDpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=29ce558c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CXRVMTjSGJ0&amp;feature=emb_err_woyt</a>"},{"pid":"ec718a5465dfeabaa4ad3bda6f9f56e0eb16e633","tid":2049515,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"無人睇"},{"pid":"a2f5c406eb0227746171dfc45950be87315f6701","tid":2049515,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e048f2d3a8171b3d52316138937fc67643e0e1e","tid":2049515,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"中国青年當年以為就咁集會可以逼中共下台<br />\n睇番係好天真"},{"pid":"3a59bcd3e57cf6650980d4f16dc4b6f523416566","tid":2049515,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3c02d661bb9666030de088ea0e5c3bd7c6cd72","tid":2049515,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0663eab8cbd681bd0a6a6fd83ff8d5a84a2f8874","tid":2049515,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47da1a2dc749943f38020ba52e0aa9d35f8cce65","tid":2049515,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"原來係區嘉雯做 今日先睇完叔叔<br />\nBtw男主角把聲咁似森美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8dde8e791db66446e9613aab9b7091c883f2bb","tid":2049515,"uid":34222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇緊"},{"pid":"10f35fc3245c5837fad24a2f794a5983fd90177c","tid":2049515,"uid":34409,"like":0,"disli